Listed on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange in October (stock code：0580.HK)






2009
Became the sole mainland provider of IGBT power modules for China CNR’s 9,600 kW electric locomotive






2008
Foundation of Wuxi Sun.King Power Capacitor Co., Ltd






2006
Research & development of ultra-voltage ETT anode saturable reactors by JS Sunking






2004
Foundation of Jiashan Sun.King Electrical Equipment & Technology 






2002
Distributor of ABB semiconductor in China
Foundation of Beijing Sun.King Power Electronic Technology Co.









