	The 15th International Exhibition on Electric Power Equipment and Technology (EP China 2014)  / The 8th International Exhibition on Electrical Equipment (Electrical China 2014) -  - SUN.KING POWER ELECTRONICS GROUP LIMITED











     
         China’s No. 1, Asia’s Leading Electric Power Exhibition
EP China & Electrical China 2014 Features 5 Theme Halls to Facilitate Business Matching
Organized by China Electricity Council & Adsale Exhibition Services Ltd, The 15th International Exhibition on Electric Power Equipment and Technology & The 8th International Exhibition on Electrical Equipment (EP China & Electrical China 2014), is the largest electric fair & electrical exhibition in China, builds on the success of EP China & Electrical China 2013. The power exhibition & electrical exhibition will be held on 22–24 Oct 2014 at China International Exhibition Center, Beijing, concurrent with 2014 International Exhibition on Electric Power Automation & Smart Grid Equipment and Technology (Electric Power Automation & Smart Grid 2014). Having the past success of EP China & Electrical China, the 2014 electric fair & electrical exhibition will gather 1000 leading exhibitors & 25000 trade buyers worldwide.
Supported by China’s major electric power group and smart grid corp, the electric fair & electrical exhibition EP China & Electrical China 2014 covers a wide scope of exhibits in electric power industry. The electric exhibition includes Power T&D, Electric Power & Power Automation, Smart Grid, Power Automation Control, Cable & accessories, Building Electrical, Power Automation Testing Equipment, Environmental Power & Smart Grid Technology.
As an international power exhibition & electrical exhibition, the electric fair EP China & Electrical China provides a one-stop platform for Power Supply Bureau & Corp, Smart Grid Construction, Manufacturer of Electric Power Equipment & Electric Power Instrumentation, Property Developer & R&D Institute with the latest technology on smart grid & power automation.
Concurrent event of the electric exhibition EP China & Electrical China is Electric Power Automation 2014. The electric exhibition shows Power T&D & Power Automation Equipment, Electric Power Automation Software, Power Distribution Automation System, Power Automation Control System & Electric Power Automation for Data Acquisition & Analysis.
Follow the trend smart grid & power automation, a new energy-saving power exhibition Smart Grid 2014 is held with the electric exhibition EP China & Electrical China. This power exhibition is the largest smart grid platform in China’s electric power industry. The electric fair & electrical exhibition displays distributed energy & smart grid equipment, smart grid dispatching, smart energy metering, smart grid security & power automation equipment.
The last electric fair & electrical exhibition EP China & Electrical China 2013 successfully held an array of symposia. In 2014, a series of seminars will be held with the power exhibition EP China & Electrical China 2014 to cover hot topics on smart grid, electric power, energy saving, power automation, electric power technology, etc.
For more info, please visit the website of the electric exhibition EP China:
www.EPChinaShow.com
Facebook
Weibo
China Electricity Council中國電力企業聯合會

















 























