                        Exhibit Product Description
                    

                        :
                    

                        Sun.King Power Electronics Group Limited is an influential supplier and integrator of systems for the power transmission and railway transportation industries. Since its establishment in 2002, the company has been rapidly growing to become a popular power electronic component supplier and a well-received power equipment and system manufacturer. Sun.King has won a great reputation in quality because we always pursue the best quality and our focus on service and win-win situation with the customers. Sun.King Power Electronics has been listed on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange since October 2010.
                    


