	sales of 1.05 billion Chinese Renmimbi [US$155.92  million]
		of which 63%
		was Electronic movie industry),
	
	Shenzhen Megmeet Electrical Co., Ltd.
	
		(1.15 billion Chinese Renmimbi [US$171.57  million]
		), and
	
	Shenzhen Absen Optoelectronic Co Ltd
	
		(1.17 billion Chinese Renmimbi [US$173.33  million]
		of which 100%
		was LED Industry).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	Sun.King Power Electronics Group Ltd reported sales of 856.95 million Chinese Renmimbi (US$127.39 million)
		for the
		
		year ending
		December of 2016.
	
		This
		
			represents
		
				an
			
			increase of 9.6%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 781.99 million Chinese Renmimbi.
	

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










